            <h1>What is Mutable?</h1><br>
            Mutable is a job board developed specifically for programmers.<br>
            It facilitates screening and hiring of programmers based on skills measured through integrated programming tasks.
        </div>
        <div class="container payload">
            <h1>How Does It Work?</h1><br>
            The entire find the job they are looking for Customize each job with a specific application, prerequisites, and programming challenges.<br>
            Programmers who are interested in the position will be able to fill out the application in a matter of minutes.<br>
            If their skills match enough of those listed in the application, they will be able to move on to step two of the application process.<br>
            Step two of the application allows the company to present the applicant with a coding challenge to prove knowledge and skills of a given language, programming paradigm, or library.<br>
            Only applicants who submit both part one and part two of the Application will be delivered to the company for review.
        </div>
